{"blogid": "126721359", "writerAge": "码龄4年", "writerBlogNum": "189", "writerCollect": "197", "writerComment": "31", "writerFan": "91", "writerGrade": "5级", "writerIntegral": "2069", "writerName": "百世经纶『一页書』", "writerProfileAdress": "..\\..\\static\\writer_image\\profile_126721359.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "10405", "writerRankWeekly": "5454", "writerThumb": "40", "writerVisitNum": "142709", "blog_read_count": "59", "blog_time": "已于 2022-09-06 13:45:58 修改", "blog_title": "Linux Mysql忘记密码，如何登录", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"../../static/bootstrap/css/csdnstyle.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"markdown_views prism-tomorrow-night\" id=\"content_views\">\n<svg style=\"display: none;\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M5,0 0,2.5 5,5z\" id=\"raphael-marker-block\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></path>\n</svg>\n<img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/9633f3bb7c3643d0a6989e51c0470ac6.gif#pic_center\"/>\n<p></p>\n<div class=\"toc\">\n<h3><font color=\"#006400\" face=\"微软雅黑\" size=\"5\">Linux Mysql忘记密码，如何登录</font></h3>\n<ul><li><ul><li><a href=\"#font_faceverdana_colorD2691E_size41Check_logfont_11\"><font color=\"#D2691E\" face=\"verdana\" size=\"4\">1.Check log</font></a></li><li><a href=\"#font_faceverdana_colorD2691E_size42Stop_mysql_serviceUpdate_configfont_19\"><font color=\"#D2691E\" face=\"verdana\" size=\"4\">2.Stop mysql service，Update config</font></a></li><li><a href=\"#font_faceverdana_colorD2691E_size43Mysql_installfont_51\"><font color=\"#D2691E\" face=\"verdana\" size=\"4\">3.Mysql install</font></a></li></ul>\n</li></ul>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<hr/>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\a4e2c743fa984909a9d7125cbe4970bd.jpeg\"/></p>\n<hr/>\n<h2><a id=\"font_faceverdana_colorD2691E_size41Check_logfont_11\"></a><font color=\"#D2691E\" face=\"verdana\" size=\"4\">1.Check log</font></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<ul><li><strong>查看状态</strong><br/> <font color=\"#FF7F50\" face=\"verdana\" size=\"4\">sudo service mysqld status</font><br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\c9f4ad09a9a042beacb6de2fa41916d6.png\"/></li><li><strong>查看初始密码</strong>（注意单引号）<br/> <font color=\"#FF7F50\" face=\"verdana\" size=\"4\">sudo grep ‘temporary password’ /var/log/mysqld.log</font><br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\d659613d81234ea188c20ec0e5056eba.png\"/></li></ul>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><a id=\"font_faceverdana_colorD2691E_size42Stop_mysql_serviceUpdate_configfont_19\"></a><font color=\"#D2691E\" face=\"verdana\" size=\"4\">2.Stop mysql service，Update config</font></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<ul><li><strong>关闭服务</strong><br/> <font color=\"#FF7F50\" face=\"verdana\" size=\"4\">sudo service mysqld stop</font></li><li><strong>修改配置文件</strong><br/> <font color=\"#FF7F50\" face=\"verdana\" size=\"4\">whereis my.cnf</font><br/> <font color=\"#FF7F50\" face=\"verdana\" size=\"4\">sudo vim /etc/my.cnf</font><br/> <strong>在mysqld标签下添加</strong><code>skip-grant-tables</code><br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\105e1cd0dd1440fda0acea4f7d61b969.png\"/></li><li><strong>重启服务</strong><br/> <font color=\"#FF7F50\" face=\"verdana\" size=\"4\">sudo service mysqld start</font><br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\51d20a75fd364b04bb98ec7f9dd065ce.png\"/></li><li><strong>访问服务</strong><br/> <font color=\"#FF7F50\" face=\"verdana\" size=\"4\">mysql -u root</font><br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\b4775fd0fe4848efa4e853f918854aaf.png\"/></li><li><strong>切换数据库</strong><br/> <font color=\"#FF7F50\" face=\"verdana\" size=\"4\">use mysql</font></li><li><strong>更改密码</strong>(注意密码的单引号)<br/> <code>update user set password=password(‘abc@123’) where user=‘root’;</code><br/> <code>update user set authentication_string=password(‘abc@123’) where user=‘root’;</code><br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\ceea2bbae9b24684bf8abbd7177c857e.png\"/></li><li><strong>刷新</strong><br/> <font color=\"#FF7F50\" face=\"verdana\" size=\"4\">flush privileges</font><br/> <font color=\"#FF7F50\" face=\"verdana\" size=\"4\">exit</font></li></ul>\n<hr/>\n<ul><li><strong>删除配置，重新登录</strong><br/> <font color=\"#FF7F50\" face=\"verdana\" size=\"4\">sudo service mysqld stop</font><br/> <font color=\"#FF7F50\" face=\"verdana\" size=\"4\">sudo vim /etc/my.cnf</font> =&gt;<code>移除前面的配置</code><br/> <font color=\"#FF7F50\" face=\"verdana\" size=\"4\">sudo service mysqld start</font><br/> <font color=\"#FF7F50\" face=\"verdana\" size=\"4\">mysql -u root -p</font></li></ul>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><a id=\"font_faceverdana_colorD2691E_size43Mysql_installfont_51\"></a><font color=\"#D2691E\" face=\"verdana\" size=\"4\">3.Mysql install</font></h2>\n<p><font color=\"#00FF00\" face=\"微软雅黑\" size=\"4\">Mysql — linux 安装(CentOS): <a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_43916074/article/details/125284109\">https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_43916074/article/details/125284109</a>.</font></p>\n</div>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/editerView/markdown_views-22a2fefd3b.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/style-4f8fbf9108.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n</div>", "first_tag": "SQL", "cpp": 0, "csharp": 0, "python": 0, "javascript": 0, "java": 0, "sql": 1, "php": 0, "time": "2022-09-06 13:45:58", "summary": "在这里插入图片描述微软雅黑忘记密码，如何登录，在这里插入图片描述查看状态在这里插入图片描述查看初始密码注意单引号在这里插入图片描述，关闭服务修改配置文件在标签下添加在这里插入图片描述重启服务在这里插入"}